*****************************************************************************************************
digiKam 5.2.0 - Release date: 2016-09-11

NEW FEATURES:

ImageEditor   : digiKam editor and Showfoto plugins interface removed to reduce run-time dependancies and speed-up initialization.
ImageEditor   : New tool to detect and fix red-eyes automatically.
Import        : New configuration options to support gPhoto2 PTP/IP cameras.
BQM           : New tool to detect and fix red-eyes automatically.
Setup         : Factoring and simplification of Album and Image Editor tabs.
Documentation : Start to re-write giant handbook based on 5.x release.


